Product:UHJvZHVjdDoxNjA4NDY=.name: Frisco Solid Nylon Dog Leash
Product:UHJvZHVjdDoxNjA4NDY=.description: Durability meets functionality with the Frisco Solid Nylon Dog Leash. This classic leash is made from a high-quality, woven nylon material and is great for everyday walks with your furry friend. Whether you’re headed to a doggie playdate or just adventuring around the block, this leash will keep your pup close by your side. The easy-to-use bolt snap securely attaches to any collar or harness, and it’s nickel-coated for a sleek, polished look. Staying in control throughout your walks will feel effortless with the handy loop that’s comfortable to grip. Leashes come in either 4- or 6-foot lengths and widths from 3/8 to 1 inch, so you’re sure to find just the right size that works for you and your pup. Frisco Solid Nylon Dog Leashes come in the same standard and vibrant color options as Frisco Solid Nylon Dog Collars, so you can color coordinate or mix and match to fit your dog’s unique style.

content.content:
|Size|Leash Length|Leash Width|Recommended Pet Weight|
|----|----|----|----|
|X-Small|6 feet|3/8 inch|up to 15 lbs|
|Small|6 feet|5/8 inch|up to 35 lbs|
|Medium|4 feet|3/4 inch|up to 50 lbs|
|Large|4 feet|1 inch|up to 80 lbs|

**Where Are Frisco Leashes Made?**

Frisco leashes are made in the USA from foreign and domestic parts. 

**Are Frisco Leashes Chew-Resistant?**

This leash is made of durable materials however, it is not chew proof. If your pet is prone to chewing, we recommend storing the leash out of reach when not in use. 

**Are Frisco Leashes Customizable?**

At this time, Frisco leashes are not customizable.  

**What Is The Best Way To Clean This Leash?**

For best results, hand wash using a mild detergent.

keyBenefits: This durable leash is made from high-quality, woven nylon that uses an Ultra-Weld™ seal for superior strength and comfort —perfect for everyday walks with your pup.
Comes in multiple lengths and widths so you can find the right fit for any size pup—choose from 4- or 6-foot lengths with widths of 3/8, 5/8, 3/4 or 1 inch.
Attaching the leash onto a collar or harness is easy with the convenient bolt snap. The clip is nickel-coated for a clean and polished look.
With a loop handle that’s easy and comfortable to grip, you can stay in control throughout the walk.
Frisco Solid Nylon Leashes come in standard and vibrant color options that match Frisco Solid Nylon Collars, so you can color coordinate or mix and match to suit your dog’s style.
